---
title: receipt_construction (osaka-blocks)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_set_succeeded : succeeded = bool
    q_set_succeeded --> q_set_gas : cumulative_gas_used = Uint
    q_set_gas --> q_set_bloom : bloom = Bloom
    q_set_bloom --> q_set_logs : logs = Tuple[Log, ...]
    q_set_logs --> q_final : freeze(Receipt)
    q_final --> [*] : done

    note right of q_set_logs
        INV: Receipt is slotted_freezable (immutable after construction)
    end note

    note right of q_set_gas
        INV: cumulative_gas_used is monotonically
        non-decreasing within a block
    end note

    note right of q_set_bloom
        INV: bloom filter must be consistent with
        the logs in this receipt
    end note
